<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>幂等 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%B9%82%E7%AD%89/</link><description>幂等 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%B9%82%E7%AD%89/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>第三方系统交互设计</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%96%B9%E6%8E%A5%E5%85%A5/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="第三方系统交互设计">第三方系统交互设计</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：与第三方系统交互的核心挑战是网络不可靠和接口差异，通过统一接口层封装异构协议，通过幂等和重试保障可靠性，通过熔断降级保障自身稳定性。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="第三方交互通过统一封装幂等重试熔断降级三大机制保障可靠性">第三方交互通过统一封装、幂等重试、熔断降级三大机制保障可靠性</h2>
<h3 id="设计原则">设计原则</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>原则</th>
          <th>说明</th>
          <th>实现</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>统一封装</td>
          <td>屏蔽第三方差异</td>
          <td>适配器模式，统一出入参</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>幂等设计</td>
          <td>重复调用无副作用</td>
          <td>业务订单号唯一性</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>超时重试</td>
          <td>网络抖动容错</td>
          <td>指数退避，限制重试次数</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>熔断降级</td>
          <td>第三方故障自我保护</td>
          <td>失败率阈值触发熔断</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>异步解耦</td>
          <td>降低耦合和延迟</td>
          <td>MQ中转</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<h3 id="接口层架构">接口层架构</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">业务层
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓ 调用
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">统一接口层（Adapter）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ├── 微信支付Adapter
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ├── 支付宝Adapter
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ├── 短信服务商Adapter
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  └── 推送服务商Adapter
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">统一接口层职责：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 入参转换（内部标准 → 第三方格式）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 出参转换（第三方格式 → 内部标准）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 签名/验签
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 超时/重试/熔断
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 日志记录</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="幂等与重试">幂等与重试</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-java">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-java" data-lang="java"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1">// 带幂等的HTTP调用</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">public</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Result</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nf">callWithRetry</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">String</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">url</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">Request</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="n">String</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">idempotencyKey</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">generateKey</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">for</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kt">int</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">i</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">=</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">0</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">i</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">MAX_RETRY</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">++</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="k">try</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="k">return</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">httpClient</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">call</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">url</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">request</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">idempotencyKey</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">TIMEOUT</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">catch</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">TimeoutException</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">{</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="k">if</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">==</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">MAX_RETRY</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">-</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">1</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">throw</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">e</span><span class="p">;</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">            </span><span class="n">Thread</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">sleep</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="kt">long</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Math</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="na">pow</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">)</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">*</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">100</span><span class="p">));</span><span class="w">  </span><span class="c1">// 指数退避</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">        </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="p">}</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="w">    </span><span class="k">throw</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="k">new</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="n">RuntimeException</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;Should not reach here&#34;</span><span class="p">);</span><span class="w">
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1第三方接口变更导致故障">问题1：第三方接口变更导致故障</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：直接依赖第三方数据结构
<strong>解决</strong>：适配器层做字段映射，变更只改适配器</p>]]></description></item><item><title>送礼系统</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E7%A4%BC%E7%89%A9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E7%A4%BC%E7%89%A9%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="送礼系统">送礼系统</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：送礼系统的核心是礼物购买、赠送、展示三个链路，通过礼物链特效增强互动体验，通过幂等设计和事务保障资金安全，通过异步消息解耦礼物展示与账户扣减。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="送礼系统通过礼物链聚合连续赠送通过事务保障资金一致通过异步解耦展示与扣减">送礼系统通过礼物链聚合连续赠送、通过事务保障资金一致、通过异步解耦展示与扣减</h2>
<h3 id="核心链路购买赠送展示结算">核心链路：购买→赠送→展示→结算</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">用户送礼流程：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 选择礼物 → 确认赠送
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 账户扣减（余额/钻石）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 本地事务：扣减用户余额 + 记录消费流水
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 礼物消息发送（MQ）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 直播间展示（礼物动画、礼物链）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">5. 主播收益结算（异步日结/实时）</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p><strong>礼物链（Gift Combo）</strong>：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">用户连续快速送同一礼物：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">送玫瑰 x1 → 展示 &#34;Tom 送出 玫瑰 x1&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">送玫瑰 x2 → 合并为 &#34;Tom 送出 玫瑰 x3&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">送玫瑰 x5 → 合并为 &#34;Tom 送出 玫瑰 x8&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">... 连续赠送合并为链式展示
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">实现：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 客户端缓存最近赠送的礼物类型
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 相同礼物在窗口期内合并计数
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 服务端验证窗口期内的总数量</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="关键设计">关键设计</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>设计点</th>
          <th>方案</th>
          <th>原因</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>幂等性</td>
          <td>礼物订单号唯一索引</td>
          <td>防重复扣款</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>扣款顺序</td>
          <td>先扣款后发MQ</td>
          <td>避免发了礼物没扣到钱</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>展示降级</td>
          <td>送礼量过大时合并显示</td>
          <td>防止客户端卡顿</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>收益结算</td>
          <td>异步日结，对账兜底</td>
          <td>实时性要求低</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1连续送礼扣款成功但展示丢失">问题1：连续送礼扣款成功但展示丢失</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：MQ消费失败或客户端丢消息
<strong>解决</strong>：MQ重试 + 客户端ACK + 对账补偿</p>]]></description></item><item><title>支付业务</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B1%82/%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="支付业务">支付业务</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：支付业务的核心挑战是资金安全和一致性，通过唯一订单号实现幂等，通过状态机管理支付生命周期，通过定时对账发现并修正差异，通过风控系统拦截可疑交易。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="支付系统通过状态机幂等设计和日终对账保障资金安全和数据一致性">支付系统通过状态机、幂等设计和日终对账，保障资金安全和数据一致性</h2>
<h3 id="支付核心流程">支付核心流程</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">支付状态机：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">INIT → 创建支付单
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">PENDING → 用户确认支付，调起渠道
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">PROCESSING → 渠道处理中
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">SUCCESS / FAIL / CLOSED
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">状态不可逆：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  SUCCESS不可变为FAIL
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  需退款走独立退款流程</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="幂等设计">幂等设计</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">支付请求：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  业务订单号 + 支付方式 + 金额 → 生成唯一支付流水号
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">重复请求处理：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 同一流水号重复请求 → 返回原结果
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - 不同流水号但同一订单 → 拒绝（防重复支付）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">实现：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  数据库唯一索引（支付流水号）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  或 Redis SETNX 分布式锁</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="对账机制">对账机制</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">日终对账流程：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 下载渠道对账单（微信/支付宝/银联）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 我方支付记录与渠道记录逐笔核对
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 金额一致 + 状态一致 → 正常
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 我方有，渠道无 → 渠道漏单，人工处理
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 渠道有，我方无 → 我方漏单，补单
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">   - 金额不一致 → 异常，人工处理
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 生成差异报表，人工确认
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 差异处理（补单/退款/调账）</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
